Homepage: https://sourceforge.net/projects/essora/
Description: EssoraKB — Graphical Kernel Builder for Essora Linux
 EssoraKB is a graphical frontend for compiling custom Linux kernels
 and generating Debian-compatible .deb packages, designed specifically
 for Essora Linux (Devuan/OpenRC based).
 .
 Features:
  - Install all kernel build dependencies in one click
  - Check missing dependencies without installing
  - Download kernel sources and compile with make bindeb-pkg
  - Generates linux-image, linux-headers, linux-kbuild and
    linux-libc-dev .deb packages ready to install
  - Pre-configured DOTconfig profiles for x86_64
  - ccache support for faster recompilation
  - Multilingual interface: en, es, fr, de, it, pt, ar, ca, hu, ru, ja, zh
  - Embedded YAD authentication dialog (no external gksu required)
  - Integrated xterm terminal with Catppuccin Mocha theme||
